<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Meals Page Revamp — Niranjan</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --ink: #0e0c0a; --paper: #f5f0e8; --dim: #9a9080;
  --gold: #c9a96e; --gold2: #e2c98a; --border: rgba(201,169,110,0.18);
  --card: #131109; --card2: #1a1712;
}
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; cursor: none; }

/* grain */
body::before { content:''; position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:9999; pointer-events:none; opacity:0.10;
  background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size:180px; }

/* cursor */
#cursor-dot,#cursor-ring { position:fixed; border-radius:50%; pointer-events:none; z-index:10000; }
#cursor-dot { width:5px; height:5px; background:var(--gold); transform:translate(-50%,-50%); }
#cursor-ring { width:32px; height:32px; border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.5); transform:translate(-50%,-50%); transition:width .25s,height .25s,border-color .25s; }
body:has(a:hover) #cursor-ring { width:48px; height:48px; border-color:var(--gold); }

/* ambient */
.ambient { position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:0; pointer-events:none; }
.ambient-blob { position:absolute; border-radius:50%; filter:blur(120px); opacity:0.06; }
.ambient-blob:nth-child(1) { width:500px; height:500px; background:#c9a96e; top:-150px; right:-80px; animation:drift1 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate; }
.ambient-blob:nth-child(2) { width:350px; height:350px; background:#6e8ec9; bottom:15%; left:-60px; animation:drift2 25s ease-in-out infinite alternate; }
@keyframes drift1 { to { transform:translate(50px,70px); } }
@keyframes drift2 { to { transform:translate(70px,-50px); } }

/* NAV */
nav { position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:500; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:20px 56px; background:rgba(14,12,10,0.75); backdrop-filter:blur(20px); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.nav-left { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:32px; }
.nav-back { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; color:var(--dim); text-decoration:none; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; transition:color .25s; }
.nav-back:hover { color:var(--gold); }
.nav-back-arrow { font-size:18px; transition:transform .25s; }
.nav-back:hover .nav-back-arrow { transform:translateX(-4px); }
.nav-logo { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:24px; font-weight:300; color:var(--paper); text-decoration:none; }
.nav-logo span { color:var(--gold); }
.nav-tag { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--dim); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:5px 14px; border-radius:20px; }

/* HERO */
.case-hero { position:relative; z-index:1; min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:flex-end; padding:140px 56px 72px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); overflow:hidden; }
.case-hero-eyebrow { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; margin-bottom:32px; }
.eyebrow-line { width:40px; height:1px; background:var(--gold); }
.eyebrow-text { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); }
.case-hero-title { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:clamp(56px,9vw,120px); font-weight:300; line-height:0.95; letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:48px; }
.case-hero-title em { font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); }
.case-hero-meta { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,auto); gap:48px; width:fit-content; }
.meta-item { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px; }
.meta-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--dim); }
.meta-value { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:18px; color:var(--paper); }
.hero-bg-num { position:absolute; right:-20px; bottom:-60px; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:clamp(120px,22vw,300px); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.02); line-height:1; pointer-events:none; letter-spacing:-0.05em; }

/* CONTENT WRAPPER */
.content { position:relative; z-index:1; }

/* SECTION DIVIDER */
.section-divider { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:80px 56px 48px; }
.divider-num { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:13px; color:var(--gold); letter-spacing:0.1em; }
.divider-title { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--dim); }
.divider-line { flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--border); }

/* TEXT SECTIONS */
.text-section { padding:0 56px 80px; max-width:900px; }
.section-kicker { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:16px; display:block; }
.section-heading { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,52px); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:24px; }
.section-heading em { font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); }
.section-body { font-size:15px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.9; }
.section-body strong { color:var(--paper); font-weight:500; }

/* STAT CALLOUT */
.stat-callout { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; max-width:900px; }
.stat-box { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:32px 36px; }
.stat-num { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:64px; font-weight:300; color:var(--gold); line-height:1; margin-bottom:10px; }
.stat-desc { font-size:13px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.6; }
.stat-desc strong { color:var(--paper); }

/* FULL-WIDTH IMAGE */
.img-full { width:100%; display:block; margin:0; }
.img-full img { width:100%; display:block; }
.img-caption { padding:16px 56px 0; font-size:12px; color:var(--dim); letter-spacing:0.06em; font-style:italic; }

/* IMAGE WITH MARGIN */
.img-section { padding:0 56px 80px; }
.img-section img { width:100%; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--border); display:block; }
.img-section-caption { margin-top:16px; font-size:12px; color:var(--dim); letter-spacing:0.06em; font-style:italic; }

/* TWO-COL IMAGES */
.img-two-col { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
.img-two-col img { width:100%; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--border); display:block; }

/* INSIGHT CARDS */
.insight-cards { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }
.insight-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }
.insight-num { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:40px; font-weight:300; color:var(--gold); line-height:1; }
.insight-title { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:20px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.3; }
.insight-title em { font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); }
.insight-body { font-size:13px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.7; }

/* PAIN POINT GRID */
.pain-grid { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
.pain-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:28px; }
.pain-card-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:16px; display:block; }
.pain-card ul { list-style:none; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
.pain-card li { font-size:13px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.6; padding-left:16px; position:relative; }
.pain-card li::before { content:'—'; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--gold); font-size:11px; }
.pain-card li strong { color:var(--paper); }

/* SOLUTION CARDS (3-col) */
.solution-cards { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }
.solution-card { border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--card); display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
.solution-card-img { width:100%; height:220px; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter:brightness(0.85); transition:filter .4s; }
.solution-card:hover .solution-card-img { filter:brightness(1); }
.solution-card-body { padding:24px; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
.solution-card-num { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:32px; font-weight:300; color:var(--gold); }
.solution-card-title { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:20px; line-height:1.25; }
.solution-card-title em { color:var(--gold); font-style:italic; }
.solution-card-desc { font-size:13px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.7; }

/* BEFORE / AFTER */
.before-after { padding:0 56px 80px; }
.before-after-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
.ba-panel { border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); }
.ba-label { padding:14px 20px; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; background:var(--card); color:var(--dim); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.ba-label.after { color:var(--gold); }
.ba-panel img { width:100%; display:block; }

/* OUTCOME */
.outcome-section { padding:0 56px 80px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; align-items:start; }
.outcome-img { border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); }
.outcome-img img { width:100%; display:block; }
.outcome-stats { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }
.outcome-stat { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:28px 32px; }
.outcome-stat-num { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:52px; font-weight:300; color:var(--gold); line-height:1; margin-bottom:8px; }
.outcome-stat-text { font-size:14px; color:var(--dim); line-height:1.7; }
.outcome-stat-text strong { color:var(--paper); }

/* NEXT PROJECT */
.next-project { margin:0 56px 80px; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:48px 56px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; text-decoration:none; color:var(--paper); background:var(--card); transition:border-color .3s, transform .3s; }
.next-project:hover { border-color:rgba(201,169,110,0.4); transform:translateY(-3px); }
.next-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--dim); margin-bottom:10px; }
.next-title { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:36px; font-weight:300; letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
.next-arrow { font-size:32px; color:var(--gold); transition:transform .3s; }
.next-project:hover .next-arrow { transform:translate(6px,-6px); }

/* FOOTER */
footer { position:relative; z-index:1; padding:40px 56px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; }
.footer-name { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:20px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(245,240,232,0.15); }
.footer-copy { font-size:11px; color:var(--dim); letter-spacing:0.08em; }

/* SCROLL REVEAL */
.reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(28px); transition:opacity .8s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1),transform .8s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); }
.reveal.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
.reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay:.1s; }
.reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay:.2s; }
.reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay:.3s; }

@media (max-width:900px) {
  nav { padding:16px 24px; }
  .nav-tag { display:none; }
  .case-hero { padding:120px 24px 56px; }
  .case-hero-meta { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:24px; }
  .section-divider,.text-section,.stat-callout,.img-section,.img-two-col,.insight-cards,.pain-grid,.solution-cards,.before-after,.outcome-section { padding-left:24px; padding-right:24px; }
  .img-full img { border-radius:0; }
  .img-caption { padding-left:24px; padding-right:24px; }
  .stat-callout,.insight-cards,.pain-grid,.solution-cards,.img-two-col,.before-after-grid,.outcome-section { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .next-project { margin:0 24px 56px; padding:32px 28px; }
  footer { padding:32px 24px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="cursor-dot"></div>
<div id="cursor-ring"></div>
<div class="ambient"><div class="ambient-blob"></div><div class="ambient-blob"></div></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-left">
    <a href="niranjan-portfolio.html" class="nav-back"><span class="nav-back-arrow">←</span> Back</a>
    <a href="niranjan-portfolio.html" class="nav-logo">N<span>.</span></a>
  </div>
  <span class="nav-tag">Case Study — 03</span>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="case-hero">
  <div class="case-hero-eyebrow">
    <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow-text">MakeMyTrip Flights · Mobile + Desktop</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="case-hero-title">Meals Page<br><em>Revamp</em> &<br>Airport Meals</h1>
  <div class="case-hero-meta">
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Company</span>
      <span class="meta-value">MakeMyTrip</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Platform</span>
      <span class="meta-value">Mobile + Desktop</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Role</span>
      <span class="meta-value">UX Designer</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Type</span>
      <span class="meta-value">UI Redesign · New Feature</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-bg-num">03</div>
</section>

<div class="content">

  <!-- ── CONTEXT ── -->
  <div class="section-divider reveal">
    <span class="divider-num">01 /</span>
    <span class="divider-title">Context</span>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-section reveal">
    <span class="section-kicker">Understanding the current scenario</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Why <em>revamp</em>?</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      The current meals section had <strong>low attach rates, very little persuasive elements</strong> and an <strong>old UI.</strong> Additionally we wanted to introduce <strong>airport meals</strong> as an option for flexible buyers who prefer to pick up food at the airport rather than commit during booking.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-03.png" alt="Current state of the meals page — existing UI across mobile and desktop">
    <p class="img-section-caption">The existing meals page across mobile and desktop — functional but lacking persuasion or discovery.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stat-callout reveal">
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">56%</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">of total bookers <strong>land on the meals page</strong> during the checkout flow.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-num">8%</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">actually think it's worth buying — they <strong>don't see any reason to stay</strong> or add a meal.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-04.png" alt="Current state data slide">
    <p class="img-section-caption">When a user lands on the meals page, they don't see any reason to stay or buy a meal.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ── RESEARCH ── -->
  <div class="section-divider reveal">
    <span class="divider-num">02 /</span>
    <span class="divider-title">Research</span>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-section reveal">
    <span class="section-kicker">User Interviews</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Understanding user <em>pain points</em> and motivations</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      We conducted user interviews to understand when people choose to buy meals, what stops them, and what would change their minds. The research surfaced clear patterns around timing, value perception, and discoverability.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="pain-grid reveal">
    <div class="pain-card">
      <span class="pain-card-label">When would users buy a meal</span>
      <ul>
        <li>Users who <strong>don't like messing with meal times</strong> during their flight</li>
        <li>During <strong>late night or early morning flights</strong> when airport outlets might be closed</li>
        <li>Short flights where they want to <strong>munch on something</strong> before reaching destination</li>
        <li>When time at the airport is less and the <strong>flight is going to be long</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <span class="pain-card-label">Problems faced by user</span>
      <ul>
        <li>Not a great value proposition — <strong>small portion, high price</strong>, questionable taste</li>
        <li>No obvious <strong>advantage to pre-booking</strong> since user will be stuck with that choice</li>
        <li>No way to know if the particular meal shown is <strong>good (review)</strong> by other users</li>
        <li>Non-indicative visual representation and <strong>lack of interesting options</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <span class="pain-card-label">Main reasons users don't buy</span>
      <ul>
        <li>Meals are a <strong>last minute thought</strong> — not something considered during booking 1–2 months prior</li>
        <li>In-flight meals are <strong>expensive and not a great value proposition</strong></li>
        <li>Users would rather eat at the airport for <strong>more options and variety</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Being stuck</strong> with the choice after pre-booking</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <span class="pain-card-label">Additional insights</span>
      <ul>
        <li>Users eat during flights <strong>out of need</strong> than want</li>
        <li>Users mostly think about meals <strong>nearer to departure</strong> than at booking time</li>
        <li>Users just need a <strong>reliable option</strong> most times</li>
        <li>Filters are <strong>not properly visible</strong> in the meals section</li>
        <li><strong>Not able to add more than 1 meal</strong> at a time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── OPPORTUNITIES ── -->
  <div class="section-divider reveal">
    <span class="divider-num">03 /</span>
    <span class="divider-title">Opportunities</span>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-section reveal">
    <span class="section-kicker">Opportunity Areas</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Deducing <em>actionable</em> insights</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Three clear opportunity areas emerged from the research — each mapping directly to a user behaviour or frustration that we could address through design.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="insight-cards reveal">
    <div class="insight-card">
      <div class="insight-num">1</div>
      <div class="insight-title"><em>Persuade</em> the users at the right moment</div>
      <div class="insight-body">Use contextual cues — like flight time, duration, or departure hour — to nudge users toward a meal at the moment it's most relevant to them.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card">
      <div class="insight-num">2</div>
      <div class="insight-title">Give <em>prominent tools and visuals</em> to find the right meal</div>
      <div class="insight-body">Better filters, food imagery, tags, and categorisation to help users quickly find something that actually appeals to them.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card">
      <div class="insight-num">3</div>
      <div class="insight-title"><em>Improve access</em> to the meal the user wants</div>
      <div class="insight-body">Introduce Airport Meals as an alternative for users who prefer flexibility — letting them pre-order from airport outlets and skip the queue.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROBLEM STATEMENT -->
  <div class="text-section reveal" style="padding-top:0; max-width:820px;">
    <span class="section-kicker">Problem Statement</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">How do we translate the <em>value of meals</em> to our users, help them find the right option or give alternative options?</h2>
  </div>

  <!-- ── SOLUTION ── -->
  <div class="section-divider reveal">
    <span class="divider-num">04 /</span>
    <span class="divider-title">What We Built</span>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-section reveal">
    <span class="section-kicker">Solution</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">The right persuasions and <em>better accessibility</em></h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      We addressed all three opportunity areas through a set of new features: a contextual persuasion carousel, an overhauled meal listing with filters and categorisation, and the all-new Airport Meals feature.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Solution 1: Contextual Persuasion -->
  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-12.png" alt="Contextual & Dynamic Persuasion — new persuasion carousel with multiple messages">
    <p class="img-section-caption">Contextual & Dynamic Persuasion — a new carousel that supports multiple persuasion messages, plus new meal tags based on popularity and airline recommendations.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Solution 2: Filters -->
  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-13.png" alt="Easy access menu and filters — new filter set and categorised menu scroller">
    <p class="img-section-caption">Easy access menu and filters — a completely new filter set plus a menu scroller with categorised listing for airlines with more than 5 meals.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Solution 3: Categorised listing -->
  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-14.png" alt="All new categorised listing with repeat orders and recommended meals">
    <p class="img-section-caption">All new categorised listing — meal categories, a "repeat order" section, and "recommended meals" surfaced prominently in the listing.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Solution 4: Airport Meals -->
  <div class="img-section reveal">
    <img src="meals-15.png" alt="Now introducing Airport Meals — pre-order from airport outlets and skip the queue">
    <p class="img-section-caption">Now introducing Airport Meals — users can pre-order from airport outlets like Vaango, Costa Coffee, Subway, and Pizza Hut, and skip the queue at the terminal.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ── BEFORE / AFTER ── -->
  <div class="section-divider reveal">
    <span class="divider-num">05 /</span>
    <span class="divider-title">Before & After</span>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

